## CORS Configuration (Backend)
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:4200,http://localhost:3000,http://127.0.0.1:4200
CORS_ALLOWED_METHODS=GET,POST,PUT,DELETE,OPTIONS
CORS_MAX_AGE=3600
CORS_ALLOW_CREDENTIALS=true
